          "source": "Glob template used to find an export by date. `{date}` is replaced with the resolved date (formatted using the date format below). `*` and `?` work as wildcards. Default `*{date}*` matches any iso.me export filename containing the date.",
          "target": "用于按日期查找导出的 Glob 模板。`{date}` 会被替换为解析后的日期（使用下方的日期格式格式化）。`*` 和 `?` 用作通配符。默认的 `*{date}*` 匹配任何包含日期的 iso.me 导出文件名。"
        },
        {
